    "The second phase involves refining this pre-trained generic GAI model using a select group of molecules with the necessary characteristics (such as bioactivity towards a specific pharmacological target).",
    "In low training data regimes, GAI models have shown potential for various applications, including generating bioactive compounds inspired by natural products and simultaneously learning many attributes.",
